    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Unlimited speed on Mitron Island!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skid Rush is an MMO racing game where you can experience various fun in the virtual open world of Mitron Island. As a resident of Mitron Island, you can engage in economic activities by carrying out missions, or you can travel around the city with friends and enjoy freedom and relaxation. Furthermore, you can form a team to compete with other teams or experience various daily life activities such as suppressing criminals in the city as a member of the government!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/780bbe3a1ddf9321dd787d093cc2f66a.poster.avif?t=1771980810\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/780bbe3a1ddf9321dd787d093cc2f66a.webm?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/780bbe3a1ddf9321dd787d093cc2f66a.mp4?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Endless fun! Explore the diverse modes of Skid Rush!!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skid Rush goes beyond simple road driving and offers thrilling racing experiences through various modes. From [Quick Service] where you quickly handle the urgent needs of Mitron Island citizens, to [Main Quest] where you protect the peace of the city amidst power struggles over Mitron Island's interests, and [Chasing Mode] where you chase and eliminate criminal vehicles (HUVs) that disrupt the order of Mitron Island! If you form a team, you can enjoy [Channel Battle] and [Tournament Championship] where you compete with other teams! Enjoy the thrill of racing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/ffe4cdb4cdb09e221fc151080a636ef1.poster.avif?t=1771980810\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/ffe4cdb4cdb09e221fc151080a636ef1.webm?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/ffe4cdb4cdb09e221fc151080a636ef1.mp4?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Create your own track and challenge yourself to a race!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From 8-lane boulevards to neighborhood alleys, all the roads in the city turn into thrilling racing tracks. Ordinary roads that you travel on every day, behind them are countless challenges and failures hidden. Create your own track that no one can easily complete and enjoy a thrilling race with others!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/84244deac11bdfa1c48715b63d9f5962.poster.avif?t=1771980810\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/84244deac11bdfa1c48715b63d9f5962.webm?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/84244deac11bdfa1c48715b63d9f5962.mp4?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Your Own Vehicle Collection and Limitless Tuning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Various types of vehicles such as sedans, SUVs, trucks, large buses, agricultural vehicles, heavy construction vehicles, supercars, and concept cars are waiting for you. Use parts to modify vehicle performance and customize the exterior with unique styling, creating your own vehicle with endless possibilities!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/010e7725c4f5c58a8fc53652d4666b75.poster.avif?t=1771980810\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/010e7725c4f5c58a8fc53652d4666b75.webm?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3063890/extras/010e7725c4f5c58a8fc53652d4666b75.mp4?t=1771980810\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></strong></strong></p>",
